t;\">药理功效：</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">果皮及果核皆可入药，果皮味苦，有利尿和消肿的功效；果核有行气、止痛、健胃消肿的功效，主治胃痛、经痛和风湿骨痛。</span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 13.63636302947998px; line-height: 19.09090805053711px;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 13.63636302947998px; line-height: 19.09090805053711px;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><span style=\"font-family: 宋体;\">夏天吃黄皮时，可以起到降火、治疗消化不良、胃脘饱胀的作用。暑天到郊外旅行，暑气迫人，倘能备带一些黄皮，尤以苦味黄皮更好，口渴或感到头脑闷热不适时，即嚼几个黄皮，不但生津、止渴，且有预防中暑的好处。</span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; font-family: tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; font-size: 13.63636302947998px; line-height: 19.09090805053711px;\"><img style=\"vertical-align: top;\" src=\"http://gd2.alicdn.com/imgextra/i2/1655466469/T2hNlOXz0aXXXXXXXX_!!1655466469.jpg\" alt=\"\" align=\"absmiddle\" /></p>','1710','美食特产	休闲零食	蜜饯/枣类/梅/果脯','广济桥牌','0','','','1','0',null,'1413679666','1413749115','1084','data/files/store_1902/goods_88/small_201410201131289229.jpg','1','1705','1706','1710','0','6.00','14','');
