e: 10pt; color: #1888c0; font-family: 宋体;\">真爱雷瑟丝</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; color: #1888c0; font-family: \'arial sans-serif\';\">)</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; color: #1888c0; font-family: 宋体;\">时常分泌一些血丝，</span></strong><strong></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; color: #1888c0; font-family: 宋体;\">何因</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; color: #1888c0; font-family: \'arial sans-serif\';\">?</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; color: #1888c0; font-family: 宋体;\">我到医院检查，无其他病症。</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; color: #525252; font-family: \'arial sans-serif\';\"><br />A: Alura</span><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; color: #525252; font-family: 宋体;\">的</span><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; color: #525252; font-family: \'arial sans-serif\';\">L-</span><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; color: #525252; font-family: 宋体;\">精胺酸经涂抹后会转换成一氧化氮，会让血管内皮细胞恢复弹性进而促进血液循环，所以初期使用会有生理周期断断续续的情况，待使用过一段时间其身体的女性荷尔蒙平衡后即会恢复原来的情况</span><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; color: #525252; font-family: \'arial sans-serif\';\">!</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; line-height: 13.5pt;\" align=\"left\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; color: #1888c0; font-family: \'arial sans-serif\';\">Q:</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; color: #1888c0; font-family: 宋体;\">我想知道</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; color: #1888c0; font-family: \'arial sans-serif\';\">Alura</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; color: #1888c0; font-family: 宋体;\">产品，对子宫内膜是否有影响，即子宫内膜是否会增厚</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; color: #1888c0; font-family: \'arial sans-serif\';\">?</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; color: #525252; font-family: \'arial sans-serif\';\"><br />A: Alura</span><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; color: #525252; font-family: 宋体;\">为一般保养品，</span><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; color: #525252; font-family: 宋体;\">是由</span><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; color: #525252; font-family: \'arial sans-serif\';\">L-</span><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; color: #525252; font-family: 宋体;\">精胺酸经涂抹后由一氧化氮转化酶转化成一氧化氮，进而促进血管内皮细胞恢复弹性而促进血液循环，但建议您先就医请医生诊断是否有其他因素以维护身体健康</span><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; color: #525252; font-family: \'arial sans-serif\';\">!!</span><br /><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; color: #525252; font-family: 宋体;\">另外因一般子宫内膜异位患者通常其免疫系统会较一般正常妇女低，也易引起其他病症的产生，建议您可以使用活力精华</span><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; color: #525252; font-family: \'arial sans-serif\';\">(Triotein)</span><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; color: #525252; font-family: 宋体;\">，活力精华</span><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; color: #525252; font-family: \'arial sans-serif\';\">(Triotein)</span><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; color: #525252; font-family: 宋体;\">主要成分为乳清蛋白，乳清蛋白可以增强人体的免疫系统，当免疫系统正常时会对到子宫腔以外的子宫内膜组织有效的监察、确认、进而摧毁之</span><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; color: #525252; font-family: \'arial sans-serif\';\">!!</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; line-height: 13.5pt;\" align=\"left\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; color: #1888c0; font-family: \'arial sans-serif\';\">Q:</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; color: #1888c0; font-family: 宋体;\">如有人问及</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; color: #1888c0; font-family: \'arial sans-serif\';\">ALURA</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; color: #1888c0; font-family: 宋体;\">该产品是否含激素问题。如何回答</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; color: #1888c0; font-family: \'arial sans-serif\';\">?</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; color: #1888c0; font-family: 宋体;\">公司该产品主要成份相互反应是否有可能合成激素类物质</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; color: #1888c0; font-family: \'arial sans-serif\';\">?</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; color: #525252; font-family: \'arial sans-serif\';\"><br />A: Alura</span><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; color: #525252; font-family: 宋体;\">是一种局部使用的乳剂，它含有微量薄荷醇及左旋精氨酸。薄荷醇