人体生理的作用颇多</span><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; color: #525252; font-family: \'arial sans-serif\';\">:</span></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; line-height: 13.5pt;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; color: #525252; font-family: \'arial sans-serif\';\">* NO</span><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; color: #525252; font-family: 宋体;\">在神经系统已被证明是一种神经传导物质，在脑神经系统中具有</span><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; color: #525252; font-family: \'arial sans-serif\';\">n-NOS</span><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; color: #525252; font-family: 宋体;\">及</span><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; color: #525252; font-family: \'arial sans-serif\';\">e-NOS</span><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; color: #525252; font-family: 宋体;\">，而其所产生的</span><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; color: #525252; font-family: \'arial sans-serif\';\">NO</span><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; color: #525252; font-family: 宋体;\">能增强</span><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; color: #525252; font-family: \'arial sans-serif\';\">long term</span><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; color: #525252; font-family: \'arial sans-serif\';\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; color: #525252; font-family: \'arial sans-serif\';\"><br />potentiation</span><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; color: #525252; font-family: 宋体;\">（</span><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; color: #525252; font-family: \'arial sans-serif\';\">LTP</span><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; color: #525252; font-family: 宋体;\">）的作用，对记忆及学习具有促进作。</span><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; color: #525252; font-family: \'arial sans-serif\';\"><br />* Nonadrenergic noncholinergic</span><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; color: #525252; font-family: 宋体;\">（</span><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; color: #525252; font-family: \'arial sans-serif\';\">NANC</span><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; color: #525252; font-family: 宋体;\">）神经，分泌</span><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; color: #525252; font-family: \'arial sans-serif\';\">NO</span><span style=\"font-size: 10pt; color: #525252; font-family: 宋体;\">促进脑血管